Interface NetworkInterfaceBase

All Superinterfaces:
HasInner<com.microsoft.azure.management.network.implementation.NetworkInterfaceInner>, HasManager<com.microsoft.azure.management.network.implementation.NetworkManager>

public interface NetworkInterfaceBase extends HasManager<com.microsoft.azure.management.network.implementation.NetworkManager>, HasInner<com.microsoft.azure.management.network.implementation.NetworkInterfaceInner>
The base network interface shared across regular and virtual machine scale set network interface.
